rows.label: qev087402_MSG0001
rows.name:
I heard he often eats breakfast here,
but...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0002
rows.name: Ah, there he is-meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0003
rows.name: Alright, let's observe him for a bit.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0004
rows.name: He's finished eating, but he's still just sitting there.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0005
rows.name: Just as Tatsu thought, he looks like he has so much of free time-meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0006
rows.name: We're having trouble with Vasalts.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0007
rows.name:
Ben, Miranda, and Cornell's teams are engaging them,
but they haven't achieved anything yet.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0008
rows.name:
Ah, Vasalt? They're easy pickin's.
Just break that single horn on their noggin.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0009
rows.name:
An orange subdermal structure gets exposed,
so just blast it with beam weapons.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0010
rows.name: Take it easy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0011
rows.name:
There's a complaint from Sakuraba Industries that the amount of Miranium
being delivered hasn't met projections.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0012
rows.name: Well, that's rough.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0013
rows.name:
For now, how 'bout increasing the
number of Data Probes, or[ST:wide ]â€”[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0014
rows.name:
figure out a clever way t' link 'em?
Isn't that worth a shot?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0015
rows.name: Somehow, there's no sense of tension-meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0016
rows.name:
Did he tell us to find him
just so he could show us this?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0017
rows.name:
Oh, you found me?
How's my elegant work this morning?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0018
rows.name: I didn't really get it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0019
rows.name:
I see, I see. Well, can't be helped.
Alright then, next I'll show ya my afternoon self.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0020
rows.name: Whaat? You're telling us watch you again?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087402_MSG0021
rows.name: That's right[ST:wait ]
